title.rendered: Nordic Compact high gloss workstation with contemporary curves and spacious storage drawer – Home Office

content.rendered:
Our Nordic Compact high gloss workstation with contemporary curves and spacious storage drawer is perfect for the home office. Made with 42mm board available in a range of finishes.

Stylish drawer spans the width of the unit and allows for maximum leg room!

Assembly required. 3 year warranty. Price is for desk only.
